title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Add a table to the report that includes a group row, a highlight rule, and a map rule. 2. Preview the report. 3. Try to export the data from the table, observe the exception being thrown.
